\begin_layout Standard
The idea of jigaw pieces with typed monopolar or bipolar connectors can
 be modelled by tensors.
 Thus, connecting two connectors (of matching type) can be understood as
 contracting a pair of tensor indexes (of the appropriate type).
 Covariant and contravariant tensor indexes are naturally bipolar (heterosexual)
 as described above; when the indexes are just 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

